{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was really-- we might have taken it serious at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it was not serious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Things began to change in the years before-- actually in the years-- in the early 1930s, Hitler came to power in 1933.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from 1930 on, it changed, because by then, many of the boys and young men had entered the Hitler guards.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very attractive to them-- beautiful uniforms and parades and all this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were indoctrinated with that violent anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, after 1933, and after the Nazis took over, the radio filled the air with anti-Semitism and with hatred and with-- and it became so that we were practically-- all of a sudden, we were boycotted and ignored.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And partially, of course, many of the boys that belonged to-- that were politically active and belonged to leftist parties were arrested.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a young man who was a good friend of mine in our business, who happened to be as a young idealistic communist.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I never talked politics with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We worked together in my father's business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And right after January 1933, he was arrested, taken to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I can still see him for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was not arrested in the-- in the office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was picked up in the morning at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And about a week later, his father came to tell my father that he was asked to pick up the ashes of his son in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the favorite excuse was saying they were shot while trying to flee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "None of them ever tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And immediately their bodies were burned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the family's were notified to pick up the ashes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
